title: Santos H. Kreimann Steps Down as Chief Executive Officer of LACERA
description: LOS ANGELES, Jan. 09, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Los Angeles County Employees Retirement Association (LACERA) today announced that Santos H. Kreimann, Chief Executive Officer, will step down from his role for health reasons and to spend more time with his family.

title: Pritzker signs major energy reform bill amid projected shortages
description: CHICAGO — Amid warnings of impending energy shortages, Gov. JB Pritzker on Thursday signed a wide-ranging energy reform package into law aimed at bolstering the state’s power grids after years of negotiations.
